<sect1>
	<title>Accessing the Program</title>
<para>
Gpe-Timetracker is accessable in the main application screen. To access it tap on the timetracker icon.
<figure>
	<title>GPE Main Screen</title>
<mediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="mainscreen.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject></mediaobject>
</figure>
<figure>
	<title>Main Application Screen</title>
<mediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="mainappscreen.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject></mediaobject>
</figure>
</para>
</sect1>
<sect1>
	<title>Icon Explanations</title>
<para>
<itemizedlist>
<listitem><mediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="blankpage.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject></mediaobject><literallayout>Create a new item to track.</literallayout></listitem>
<listitem><mediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="delete.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject></mediaobject><literallayout>Delete a selected item.</literallayout></listitem>
<listitem><mediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="clock.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject></mediaobject><literallayout>Clock in.</literallayout></listitem>
<listitem><mediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="stop_clock.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject></mediaobject><literallayout>Clock out.</literallayout></listitem>
<listitem><mediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="list-view.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject></mediaobject><literallayout>Show the logged info.</literallayout></listitem>
</itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect1>
<sect1>
	<title>Using the Application</title>
<para>
<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para> To clock in on an item select it form the list and then tap on the clock with the green check mark.</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>To clock out of an item tap on the clock with the red x.</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>When clocking in or out you are given the option for notes pertaining to the task.</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>It is possible to add a sub item. Simply tap on the desired field and tap on the blank page icon and enter in a name.</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>To add more notes about the item tap on the edit icon.</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>To delete the item tap on the trash can.</para></listitem>
</itemizedlist>
